body:
@mrry I started from `tf.data.from_generator` and wrote a wrapper around `pyfunc` to allow nested structures. Should I make a PR?

Further, I have now also a `tf.data.from_indexable` (Only some few lines with range and map) that support parallel loading with python code. Should I make a PR, else I will keep the code in my own code base?
